sub_title: Professor in Maintenance at Netherlands Defence Academy & University of Twente
summary:
Tiedo Tinga is lecturing and executing / supervising research projects on all technical aspects of maintenance, in which he is trying to integrate the various disciplines of maintenance.

Specialties: structural integrity, materials modelling, physics of failure, reliability engineering, condition based maintenance, structural health monitoring
